data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION.   Great living space inside and out in this 2 story home with a twist.   There is a spacious  family  room to enjoy family time with plenty of room for everyone to gather.  Or for more intimate evenings, gather around the gas fireplace in the gathering  room off the kitchen area.  Looking for more space to spread out? We got that too! There is a lower level rec room guest room and  3/4 bath. The outdoor living space includes a large covered back deck and a salt water in ground pool with slide. Oh, and did I mention the 3 car garage for cars and toys?   Yes, we have that too. All this is situated on a corner lot in the sub division of Sylvan Heights. Convenient to all the local amenities: restaurants, parks and the mall.
